1
00:00:19,162 --> 00:00:24,349
♪The whole world is lit up♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
♪Because you exist♪

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
♪You're always♪

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
♪Hold tight♪

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,007
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 19=

9
00:00:48,299 --> 00:00:49,339
Wait.

10
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:58,578
Everyone, I also have something

11
00:00:58,579 --> 00:01:00,140
I'd like to show you.

12
00:01:01,619 --> 00:01:02,939
Please, look at these.

13
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:04,058
These documents

14
00:01:04,059 --> 00:01:07,218
record that the Acting President
of Mu Group, Xu Mingzhu, is suspected

15
00:01:07,219 --> 00:01:10,140
(Authentic painting)
of commissioning others to forge paintings.

16
00:01:11,660 --> 00:01:13,138
And the fake painting she forged

17
00:01:13,139 --> 00:01:14,459
is exactly the work

18
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:17,338
that Mr. Hong is about to release

19
00:01:17,339 --> 00:01:18,939
at the Mu Group's exclusive auction.

20
00:01:19,059 --> 00:01:19,819
Ms. Xu,

21
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:20,299
this...

22
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:21,900
How could this be?

23
00:01:22,540 --> 00:01:24,420
I wonder what explanation

24
00:01:24,499 --> 00:01:26,260
you have for this matter, Ms. Xu?

25
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:30,099
(So you deliberately set me up.)

26
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:34,011
How could you possibly get my signature?

27
00:01:34,012 --> 00:01:34,811
Unless it was Shen...

28
00:01:34,812 --> 00:01:35,692
Who?

29
00:01:38,460 --> 00:01:40,220
Ms. Xu, look closely.

30
00:01:40,619 --> 00:01:41,819
On these documents,

31
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:43,620
there is only your signature.

32
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:49,539
It's you.

33
00:01:50,619 --> 00:01:52,459
You're all in this together to ruin me.

34
00:01:55,979 --> 00:01:57,418
You want to destroy my reputation

35
00:01:57,419 --> 00:01:58,860
and force me out of the group.

36
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:03,379
How despicable.

37
00:02:03,419 --> 00:02:04,459
Despicable?

38
00:02:05,219 --> 00:02:06,939
You're the despicable one here,

39
00:02:07,300 --> 00:02:08,140
Ms. Xu.

40
00:02:08,812 --> 00:02:10,098
Why don't you think hard

41
00:02:10,099 --> 00:02:11,395
about what you've done?

42
00:02:13,819 --> 00:02:14,659
Everyone,

43
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,659
regarding this matter,

44
00:02:16,819 --> 00:02:19,340
Mu Group will definitely
give you all an explanation.

45
00:02:19,779 --> 00:02:20,699
Ms. Xu,

46
00:02:20,939 --> 00:02:22,218
you should also think hard

47
00:02:22,219 --> 00:02:23,979
about how to explain this to the board.

48
00:02:25,625 --> 00:02:26,819
Mu Zhiyu,

49
00:02:27,499 --> 00:02:29,340
who wins and who loses,

50
00:02:30,075 --> 00:02:31,460
it is yet to be decided.

51
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,849
(Moser International)
Xu Mingzhu

52
00:02:36,850 --> 00:02:38,291
is truly too much.

53
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,498
How could she do

54
00:02:39,499 --> 00:02:41,419
something so damaging to Mu Group?

55
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:42,378
If you ask me,

56
00:02:42,379 --> 00:02:44,579
we should just
remove her from her position.

57
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:47,539
Let Zhiyu serve
as our group's president.

58
00:02:47,659 --> 00:02:49,020
This is also equivalent

59
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:52,020
to inheriting Chairman Mu's position.

60
00:02:52,939 --> 00:02:54,658
(Zhiyu finally turned the tables.)

61
00:02:54,659 --> 00:02:55,900
(I hope everything goes well.)

62
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:58,250
Holding a board meeting
without notifying me?

63
00:02:58,819 --> 00:02:59,740
Xu Mingzhu.

64
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:00,818
Ms. Xu,

65
00:03:00,819 --> 00:03:03,539
shouldn't you give us an explanation
about the fake painting?

66
00:03:03,575 --> 00:03:05,659
I indeed have to explain it well.

67
00:03:08,499 --> 00:03:10,098
I have an important document here

68
00:03:10,099 --> 00:03:11,500
to announce.

69
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:14,379
(Does she still have a trump card?)

70
00:03:16,099 --> 00:03:17,261
Take a look first.

71
00:03:17,262 --> 00:03:19,470
(DNA Test Report)

72
00:03:19,850 --> 00:03:21,778
This is a DNA test.

73
00:03:21,779 --> 00:03:23,259
The results show

74
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:25,311
that Mu Zhiyu is not the daughter

75
00:03:25,312 --> 00:03:26,833
of Mu Group's Chairman Mu Chenzhou.

76
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,869
In other words,

77
00:03:28,939 --> 00:03:30,179
(DNA Test Report)
she is not

78
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,480
(Blood, taken from Mu Chenzhou and Mu Zhiyu)
the heiress to Mu Group at all.

79
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,424
This...

80
00:03:33,425 --> 00:03:34,845
(No biological relationship
between Mu Chenzhou and Mu Zhiyu.)

81
00:03:35,939 --> 00:03:38,419
(I'm actually not
Mu Chenzhou's daughter?)

82
00:03:39,379 --> 00:03:39,859
(Oh no.)

83
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:42,259
(How did Xu Mingzhu
find out about Zhiyu's birth?)

84
00:03:42,499 --> 00:03:44,498
(Swapping those two children back then)

85
00:03:44,499 --> 00:03:46,338
(was meant for
a counterattack like today)

86
00:03:46,339 --> 00:03:47,774
(to protect myself.)

87
00:03:47,775 --> 00:03:50,658
(The wedding is off,
and the inheritance is gone.)

88
00:03:50,659 --> 00:03:52,580
(But I am Mu Chenzhou's wife.)

89
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:55,819
(I can still
naturally inherit Mu Group.)

90
00:03:56,700 --> 00:03:59,019
How could Zhiyu
not be the heiress of the Mu family?

91
00:03:59,020 --> 00:04:02,620
It's there in black and white with
hospital certification. This can't be faked.

92
00:04:05,339 --> 00:04:06,580
Mu Zhiyu,

93
00:04:07,219 --> 00:04:09,498
you clearly knew
you weren't Mu Chenzhou's daughter,

94
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:11,259
yet you still schemed
to return to the country

95
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:13,020
to seize Mu Group.

96
00:04:14,787 --> 00:04:17,306
I will never let Mu Group

97
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:19,340
fall into the hands of someone like you.

98
00:04:21,612 --> 00:04:22,292
This...

99
00:04:22,979 --> 00:04:24,459
Rest assured, directors.

100
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:26,338
I will immediately
hold a press conference

101
00:04:26,339 --> 00:04:28,739
to officially take over
Mu Group as Chairman.

102
00:04:29,179 --> 00:04:30,619
As for Mu Zhiyu,

103
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,179
since she's not
a member of the Mu family,

104
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:37,020
she has no right
to stay in Mu Group anymore.

105
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:58,800
♪Listen, the wind chime is ringing♪

106
00:04:58,875 --> 00:05:02,178
♪I wish to forget you♪

107
00:05:02,179 --> 00:05:03,099
Zhiyu,

108
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:06,139
there must be another way to solve this.

109
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,099
Trust me,

110
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,099
I will always be by your side.

111
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:14,499
♪The scenery you once said
you wanted to see♪

112
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:17,218
♪You asked me to see it for you instead♪

113
00:05:17,219 --> 00:05:18,739
Actually, regarding this matter,

114
00:05:19,637 --> 00:05:21,238
I've had my suspicions.

115
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:26,220
I just felt

116
00:05:26,859 --> 00:05:27,900
that my dad...

117
00:05:28,299 --> 00:05:29,340
His behavior,

118
00:05:29,512 --> 00:05:30,785
personality, and temperament,

119
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:32,539
we were nothing alike.

120
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:34,236
I always thought

121
00:05:34,237 --> 00:05:35,238
it might be

122
00:05:36,387 --> 00:05:38,179
because I'm a girl.

123
00:05:39,175 --> 00:05:40,456
So,

124
00:05:40,979 --> 00:05:43,019
I worked even harder to prove myself.

125
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:45,502
♪Your freedom♪

126
00:05:47,419 --> 00:05:48,979
Sometimes, I think

127
00:05:51,037 --> 00:05:53,419
how great it would be
if I weren't a Mu child.

128
00:05:57,275 --> 00:05:58,556
But over these years,

129
00:05:58,700 --> 00:06:00,340
whether as an auctioneer

130
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:02,619
or returning to the Mu Group
to handle things,

131
00:06:02,625 --> 00:06:04,220
you have done very well.

132
00:06:04,900 --> 00:06:06,549
You've already proven yourself.

133
00:06:06,550 --> 00:06:12,461
♪When I look up,
it would shine like the stars♪

134
00:06:12,462 --> 00:06:16,645
♪But you forgot to teach me♪

135
00:06:16,779 --> 00:06:18,859
But I really am not
a member of the Mu family.

136
00:06:23,099 --> 00:06:24,379
When Xu Mingzhu brought out

137
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:26,419
that DNA test result,

138
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:27,499
it felt like it proved

139
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:29,579
everything I've worked
for all these years

140
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:31,380
was all just a joke.

141
00:06:32,299 --> 00:06:34,340
Fighting her for
the Mu Group for so long

142
00:06:37,539 --> 00:06:39,020
was also a joke.

143
00:06:39,859 --> 00:06:40,820
Zhiyu,

144
00:06:41,979 --> 00:06:42,979
look at me.

145
00:06:43,779 --> 00:06:44,900
Look at me.

146
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:49,979
Pull yourself together.

147
00:06:52,779 --> 00:06:54,580
Think about what kind
of person Xu Mingzhu is.

148
00:06:55,099 --> 00:06:56,979
If the Mu Group is handed over to her,

149
00:06:57,099 --> 00:06:58,260
it'll be over.

150
00:07:00,739 --> 00:07:02,658
This isn't just about Mu Chenzhou

151
00:07:02,659 --> 00:07:03,619
or the Mu family.

152
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:06,739
It's the life's work
of your mother and grandfather

153
00:07:06,979 --> 00:07:08,979
over all these years.

154
00:07:11,150 --> 00:07:13,191
Can you really bear
to see it go to waste?

155
00:07:25,099 --> 00:07:26,940
But I'm no longer
a member of the Mu family.

156
00:07:27,687 --> 00:07:29,746
I have no right to fight for it.

157
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,699
I want to be alone.

158
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:35,739
You should go.

159
00:07:38,150 --> 00:07:39,983
(Zhiyu, don't be sad.)

160
00:07:40,179 --> 00:07:41,380
(From now on,)

161
00:07:41,580 --> 00:07:44,700
(it's my turn
to stand up and protect you.)

162
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,139
Ms. Xu,

163
00:07:50,140 --> 00:07:52,479
is the press conference you called today
to clarify the matter

164
00:07:52,479 --> 00:07:53,824
of intentionally forging a painting

165
00:07:53,825 --> 00:07:55,705
to sabotage the Hong auction?

166
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,338
The previous incident

167
00:07:58,339 --> 00:08:00,658
was purely malicious
exploitation by someone.

168
00:08:00,659 --> 00:08:03,136
The Mu Group
will provide an explanation.

169
00:08:03,137 --> 00:08:04,896
But what I want to announce today

170
00:08:04,897 --> 00:08:05,977
is far more important.

171
00:08:06,262 --> 00:08:08,800
Mu Group's Business Director, Mu Zhiyu,

172
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,800
who is also known
as the daughter of the Mu family,

173
00:08:11,525 --> 00:08:13,780
is not the heiress to our Mu family.

174
00:08:14,820 --> 00:08:15,619
Is that true?

175
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:16,524
Really, Ms. Xu?

176
00:08:16,525 --> 00:08:18,811
Is Mu Zhiyu really
not the heiress to the Mu family?

177
00:08:18,812 --> 00:08:20,859
Miss Mu, do you have anything to say?

178
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:22,739
It is absolutely true.

179
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:25,019
The directors are already aware of this.

180
00:08:25,020 --> 00:08:26,218
So now,

181
00:08:26,219 --> 00:08:28,580
representing the Mu Group,
I solemnly declare

182
00:08:28,979 --> 00:08:30,499
that Mu Zhiyu will...

183
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,220
Hold on.

184
00:08:48,512 --> 00:08:50,952
(Jibai? Why is he here?)

185
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,580
Before announcing the results,

186
00:08:56,620 --> 00:08:58,700
everyone, why don't
you look at this first?

187
00:09:00,459 --> 00:09:01,219
I have here

188
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:03,698
(DNA Test Report)
a hospital-certified paternity test result.

189
00:09:03,699 --> 00:09:04,779
It proves

190
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:08,010
that I am the biological son
of Mu Chenzhou.

191
00:09:09,075 --> 00:09:10,686
That is to say, I am the Mu heir

192
00:09:10,687 --> 00:09:12,808
whose identity was deliberately switched

193
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,460
by someone years ago.

194
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,770
(Is this kid crazy?)

195
00:09:23,459 --> 00:09:24,058
Ms. Xu,

196
00:09:24,059 --> 00:09:25,499
is what this gentleman said true?

197
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,580
Who exactly is the heir to the Mu Group?

198
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,420
Shen Jibai,

199
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,938
even if you want
to stand up for Mu Zhiyu,

200
00:09:31,939 --> 00:09:33,820
you don't need
to use such lowly tactics.

201
00:09:34,459 --> 00:09:35,979
Seeing me bring out a paternity test,

202
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,499
you bring one out too?

203
00:09:37,659 --> 00:09:39,300
Isn't that a bit too childish?

204
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,619
Ms. Xu,

205
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:42,300
what are you nervous about?

206
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:46,019
If you all don't believe it,

207
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,220
you can look at this.

208
00:09:47,537 --> 00:09:49,640
(Electronic Account)
These are transfer records between

209
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:52,580
my adoptive mother, Shen Yi, and the
Mu Group's Vice President, Xu Mingzhu.

210
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:54,499
Ms. Xu,

211
00:09:55,562 --> 00:09:57,624
why were you transferring money
to my adoptive mother?

212
00:09:57,625 --> 00:09:59,178
(How is this possible?)

213
00:09:59,179 --> 00:10:01,739
(I clearly investigated
and confirmed repeatedly)

214
00:10:01,779 --> 00:10:04,361
(that the Mu family boy had died in the streets
fighting underground long ago.)

215
00:10:04,362 --> 00:10:05,483
Furthermore,

216
00:10:05,819 --> 00:10:06,698
Xu Mingzhu,

217
00:10:06,699 --> 00:10:09,339
your initial hire of me
as the Head of Security for Mu Group

218
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:11,086
was just so I could
get close to Mu Zhiyu

219
00:10:11,087 --> 00:10:13,460
and obtain information
about the Mu Group inheritance.

220
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:14,849
Now,

221
00:10:14,850 --> 00:10:17,329
I am the only
biological son of Mu Chenzhou.

222
00:10:17,939 --> 00:10:19,820
According to
the inheritance regulations,

223
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,300
I

224
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:24,340
am the true heir of the Mu Group.

225
00:10:37,962 --> 00:10:42,192
♪Light comes beaming in♪

226
00:10:42,332 --> 00:10:46,701
♪Landing on my skin♪

227
00:10:46,702 --> 00:10:51,192
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

228
00:10:55,412 --> 00:10:59,351
♪Shadows move around♪

229
00:10:59,352 --> 00:11:03,961
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

230
00:11:03,962 --> 00:11:08,492
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

231
00:11:12,092 --> 00:11:17,882
♪Don't slip away♪

232
00:11:20,332 --> 00:11:24,901
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

233
00:11:24,902 --> 00:11:29,301
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

234
00:11:29,302 --> 00:11:33,622
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

235
00:11:33,642 --> 00:11:37,622
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

236
00:11:38,092 --> 00:11:42,401
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

237
00:11:42,402 --> 00:11:46,731
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

238
00:11:46,732 --> 00:11:51,041
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

239
00:11:51,042 --> 00:11:57,192
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪
